snippet.title: PULSO POP NEWS
snippet.description:
Headquartered in Miami with reporters in Los Angeles and New York, PulsoPOP delivers fresh, trending, and exclusive entertainment news and interviews curated for all Latino generations, especially LatinX millennials and Gen Z! 

Check us out at WWW.PULSOPOP.COM | follow us @PULSOPOPNEWS
